text: Coronation Park is windy and serene. It's suitable for young kids to play. Adults can also use the outdoor gym for exercise. There's pavilion for resting. The benches are also nice to sit. It's also suitable for dogs to rest and enjoy

Loving the new upgrades to the park! The kids affectionately calls it their pirate ship! Although the grass patch was taken up to build the playground, I'm sure the kids don't mind. Kids did complain that there were only 2 swings and none for babies. There are also no seats around the park for the caregivers/ parents.

Pretty nice sedate Park when I visited it at 9pm on 17 February 2023.

Nice place to exercise if you live around the vicinity.
Is good  play with kids same time doing exercises

Used to be where my kindergarten was. It's really a kid and elderly playground. There is no fitness corner for pull up or dips.
But I guess the kids like the upgrade.
Every Thurs evening around 7pm, there is zumba session too.
